        <div class="security-card">
          <div class="security-icon">🔐</div>
          <h3>Personal Gate Code</h3>
          <p>Every customer receives their own unique gate code at move-in. No shared combinations, no master keys handed out at a front desk. Your code is yours alone, and it works around the clock.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="security-card">
          <div class="security-icon">🚧</div>
